Introducing our projects
ShadowCast
We will create high-quality video content about NFTs.
It’s going to be YouTube channel “ShadowCast”, where we speak on topics like: where to find upcoming collections how to analyse collections, how to create collection, etc.
And of course there will be exclusive content only for holders. We will invite cool people from NFT space to talk to them about industry.
Shadow Tools
We are creators not only in art space. We love to build services that help people. We are developing several tools for NFT traders and NFT collectors.
We’ve already created telegram bot, that notifies about upcoming collections. Check it out.
ShadowVerse
We’ll also tell more about ShadowVerse and create a game.
Our vision is that games should bring joy and fun, they are not meant to be places for grind or work. So we don’t want to use classical P2E mechanics for NFT games. Instead of this we want to focus on what NFTs do very good – creating closed communities.
We’ll deliver new content every couple of months, so the holders will constantly get new gaming experience.
